IMPORTANT NOTICE - RESPONSIBLE USE

This software is designed for educational purposes with explicit consent.
The use of this software without proper consent or for surveillance purposes
goes against the project's purpose and may violate privacy laws.

Users must:
- Obtain explicit consent from all monitored individuals
- Clearly communicate what data is collected and why
- Provide transparent opt-out mechanisms
- Comply with applicable privacy laws and regulations
- Use the software only in educational contexts with proper supervision

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any
misuse or violation of privacy laws resulting from improper use of this software.